Your aim is to decipher an encrypted text which will take you to the solution of the challenge. First of all you need to know that, right now, only a certain number of users should know for sure the cipher used in this challenge. Why? <a href="http://www.bright-shadows.net/challenges/special_occio/Challenges.htm" class="challenge_1">Discover</a> it!<br /><br />
Then only enter the name of the cipher plus the first two letters of a username... you should know which one. ;)<br />
For example:<p class="challenge_1" style="text-align:center;">If the cipher is a simple substitution and the username is &quot;cartodd&quot; we have: &quot;simplesubstitutionca&quot;.</p>
Is it clear enough? Well, good luck!<br />
